{"id":18935,"title":"Joint failure after steroid therapy in tuberculous encephalitis.","abstract":"We report a case of multifocal avascular osteonecrosis (AVN) following steroid administration in a case of tuberculous encephalitis in a young patient. The risk of joint-related AVN as a side effect of adjunctive steroid therapy should be taken into consideration when evaluating the dosage and treatment duration in tuberculous encephalitis.","date":"2014-06-16","categories":"Bacterial Infections and Mycoses","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24754480","annotations":[{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.801843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Epileptic seizure","weight":0.734911,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Epileptic_seizure"},{"name":"Side effect","weight":0.70516,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Side_effect"},{"name":"Joint","weight":0.683457,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joint"},{"name":"Encephalitis","weight":0.668553,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Encephalitis"},{"name":"Blood vessel","weight":0.651693,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blood_vessel"},{"name":"Tuberculosis","weight":0.630211,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tuberculosis"},{"name":"Dose (biochemistry)","weight":0.541196,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dose_(biochemistry)"},{"name":"Steroid","weight":0.537421,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Steroid"},{"name":"Patient","weight":0.418173,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patient"},{"name":"Avascular necrosis","weight":0.415777,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Avascular_necrosis"},{"name":"Risk","weight":0.146903,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Risk"},{"name":"Adjunct (grammar)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adjunct_(grammar)"},{"name":"Time","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia